{"tid":974714,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"KPOP港女 CLC月内攜新專輯回歸！網傳銷量不過兩萬要解散","createTime":"2019-01-09T05:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T17:42:15.000Z","uid":74065,"like":31,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3c09181ebdc0aae1c5506e3fbec442e4b28d309a","tid":974714,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T05:47:58.000Z","msg":"CLC早前在團體綜藝《城東居民CLC》中播出了錄音的場景，卻收到回歸延遲的消息。她們所錄的歌曲，其後被爆成為IZ*ONE的出道歌《La Vie en Rose》，令粉絲十分心疼。不過，她們所屬的CUBE娛樂證實CLC將要在本月内回歸，總算有喜訊了！<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/01/20190109_EN_CLC_4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F01%2F20190109_EN_CLC_4.jpg&h=9b38896a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n昨日（8日）有多個韓國媒體引述歌謠界人士的消息，指CLC將於1月底發行新專輯，目前也為這個目標加緊準備回歸。其後，CUBE娛樂出面證實消息，指CLC確實會在月内回歸。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/01/20190109_EN_CLC_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F01%2F20190109_EN_CLC_2.jpg&h=5d5780ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這也是CLC去年2月發表第7張迷你專輯《BLACK DRESS》後，時隔近一年的回歸。但網上也流傳如果CLC這次的專輯銷售若果無法破兩萬張，CUBE娛樂會考慮解散組合，所以各位粉絲也要好好支持成員了！<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/01/20190109_EN_CLC_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F01%2F20190109_EN_CLC_1.jpg&h=d3d8870e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n笑下笑下 可能真係最後機會"},{"pid":"9fb8456a34db3abc285742758d58b801a1097abf","tid":974714,"uid":223790,"like":2,"dislike":21,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"